OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,FA deal to sell ITV's channels to Sky is
OL,7,Freportedly imminent.
OL,9,FThe final agreement is said to be under
OL,10,Fscrutiny by the companies' lawyers.
OL,12,FIt could be announced to the stock
OL,13,Fmarket within the next week or two.
OL,15,FWhen this happens, there needs to be
OL,16,Fproper scrutiny over the implications
OL,17,Ffor ITV 1's public service obligations.
OL,19,FIn particular there must be clear lines
OL,20,Fin the sand on:
OL,23,EPub: 28-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14202
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1782942089
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,F- The minimum amount of national news
OL,7,Fon ITV 1.
OL,9,F- The number of regional news services
OL,10,Fin England plus the minimum amount in
OL,11,Feach area.
OL,13,F- The minimum amount of bespoke output
OL,14,F` including news and other programmes `
OL,15,Fin Wales and Northern Ireland.
OL,17,FThe recent changes to STV's legal
OL,18,Frequirements mean there can be no
OL,19,Fpresumptions that the status quo will
OL,20,Fremain until 2034.
OL,23,EPub: 28-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14203
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1782942089
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,7,Fhas the power to block the deal or
OL,8,Fimpose conditions. Ofcom is not as
OL,9,Fpowerless as its critics suggest either
OL,10,F` it watered down some of STV's recent
OL,11,Fproposals.
OL,13,FThe CMA and Ofcom could insist that
OL,14,Fthere should be no changes to PSB
OL,15,Frequirements for, say, 5 years.
OL,17,FIf there is a case for a specific
OL,18,Fchange ` say a complete standardisation
OL,19,Fof the volumes in Wales and NI ` that
OL,20,Fcould be debated and decided ahead of
OL,21,Fthe deal.
OL,23,EPub: 28-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14204
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1782942089
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,FGuarantees should be required that the
OL,7,FITV News service ` currently provided
OL,8,Fby ITN ` must remain entirely separate
OL,9,Ffrom Sky News for now.
OL,11,FWhen ITN's current contract is up,
OL,12,Fthere should be a fair tendering
OL,13,Fprocess with no presumed outcome.
OL,15,FITV's wider contribution to creative
OL,16,Findustries needs protected too.
OL,18,FThere must be guarantees concerning the
OL,19,Fproportion of the schedule devoted to
OL,20,Foriginal UK output. In particular, some
OL,21,Fof it must clearly be of high quality.
OL,23,EPub: 28-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14205
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1782942089
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,FThink of the risks if guarantees aren't
OL,7,Fmade.
OL,9,F- Sky News going out on ITV 1 ` meaning
OL,10,Fsignificant job losses and a reduction
OL,11,Fin plurality.
OL,13,F- The BBC left as the only high quality
OL,14,Fprovider of regional news and bespoke
OL,15,Fcontent for the nations.
OL,17,F- A greater proportion of the ITV 1
OL,18,Fschedule being filled by imports or
OL,19,Fcheap material.
OL,21,FThese bad outcomes are not inevitable
OL,22,Fbut there are real risks.
OL,23,EPub: 28-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
