OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCRegulators must not wave
OL,4,Cthrough the Sky-ITV deal
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe government and Ofcom need to act
OL,7,Fnow to prevent these things from
OL,8,Fhappening ` they cannot wait until it
OL,9,Fis too late.
